These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-1::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, raspberry, strawberry, eggplant
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, french, indian, nigerian
1. the person eating raspberry is somewhere to the right of the person eating spinach##5
2. the nigerian is on the left or right of the brazilian##3
3. the brazilian is in an odd position##4
4. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the nigerian##5
5. the brazilian is the person eating raspberry##1
6. the person eating strawberry is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Food      | eggplant  | spinach | raspberry  | strawberry |
| Nationality   | indian | nigerian      | brazilian | french |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-2::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, lemon, eggplant, onion
4 different pets are kept: bird, chinchilla, goat, horse
1. the person eating lemon is between the owner of the bird and the owner of the horse##2
2. the person eating onion is somewhere to the left of the owner of the horse##5
3. the owner of the bird is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
4. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person eating onion##1
5. the owner of the chinchilla is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Food   | onion | eggplant | lemon   | strawberry |
| Pet           | goat      | bird    | chinchilla | horse      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-3::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, corn, peach, potato
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, scientific, superhero, musical
1. the person eating corn is the person watching scientific movies##1
2. the person watching musical movies is on the right of the person eating corn##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching zombie movies##5
4. the person watching zombie movies is on the left or right of the person eating peach##3
5. the person eating potato is somewhere to the right of the person watching musical movies##5
6. the person eating corn is somewhere to the left of the person watching superhero movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |    2    |     3     |   4    |
| Food        | corn | cabbage | peach     | potato |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific  | musical   | superhero | zombie    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, singing, skydiving, woodworking
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: dahlia, orchid, zinnia, marigold
1. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the right of the person who growszinnia##5
3. the person who's hobby is card-games is between the person who growsmarigold and the person who growsorchid##2
4. the person who growszinnia is on the left or right of the person who growsmarigold##3
5. the person who growsmarigold is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | skydiving | card-games | singing | woodworking |
| Flower   | marigold   | zinnia     | orchid    | dahlia       |

