.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-5::.
There 4 different types of food: banana, corn, eggplant, kale
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, golf, climbing, soccer
1. the person eating kale is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##5
2. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating eggplant##3
3. the person eating eggplant is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
4. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person eating corn##3
6. the person eating kale is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |    3     |    4    |
| Food          | eggplant | kale   | banana   | corn    |
| Sport   | golf  | soccer | ice-hockey | climbing |

