.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-6::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, firefighter, paramedic, police-officer
There are 4 different favourite beverages: sprite, cola, coffee, hot-chocolate
1. the police-officer is in an odd position##4
2. the electrician is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the police-officer and the person drinking coffee##2
4. the paramedic is on the right of the person drinking sprite##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |       3        |     4     |
| Job           | electrician | firefighter | police-officer | paramedic |
| Beverage   | coffee        | hot-chocolate     | sprite       | cola   |

