.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-8::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, mango, pear, strawberry
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, coffee, juice, water
1. the person drinking coffee is on the right of the person drinking water##1
2. the person eating strawberry is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5
3. the person eating strawberry is on the left or right of the person eating pear##3
4. the person eating mango is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the person drinking juice is somewhere to the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##5

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Food   | mango     | strawberry | pear     | carrot   |
| Beverage    | water | coffee  | juice | hot-chocolate |

