The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, martial-arts, comedy, romance
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
4. the person drinking cola is somewhere to the right of the person watching romance movies##5
5. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching action movies##5
6. the person watching action movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching comedy movies##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |    2     |   3    |  4   |
| Beverage   | almond-milk | iced-tea | milk   | cola |
| Movie-Genre       | action       | comedy   | romance | martial-arts |

