.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, tea
4 different pets are kept: rat, horse, dog, pony
1. the person drinking mirinda is on the left or right of the owner of the horse##3
2. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person drinking tea##5
3. the owner of the pony is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the right of the owner of the pony##5
5. the owner of the horse is somewhere to the left of the person drinking cola##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |   3    |     4      |
| Beverage   | iced-tea | mirinda       | cola   | tea        |
| Pet      | horse  | pony | rat | dog |

