.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-11::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, january, february, july
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, soccer, water-polo
1. the person who's birthday is in august is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in january##5
2. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person who's birthday is in january##1
4. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is soccer##5
5. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is badminton##5
6. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is parkour##3
7. the person who's birthday is in february is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is badminton##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |    3    |     4      |
| Birthday   | august | january   | february | july     |
| Sport   | parkour     | badminton | soccer  | water-polo |

