.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-12::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, card-games, writing, gardening
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, golf, lacrosse, skateboarding
1. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is skateboarding is in an even position##4
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is golf##5
4. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person who's sport is lacrosse##1
5. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is writing##5
6. the person who's sport is golf is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |     3      |  4   |
| Hobby   | magic-tricks | writing        | gardening        | card-games |
| Sport         | lacrosse  | skateboarding | basketball | golf |

