.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-13::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: camping, dancing, woodworking, writing
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, skateboard, subway, car
1. the person driving the skateboard is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
2. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the person driving the snowmobile##5
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is woodworking is somewhere to the left of the person driving the car##5
5. the person driving the car is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
| Hobby         | woodworking | writing | dancing | camping |
| Transport   | snowmobile     | car  | skateboard  | subway    |

