4. the mexican is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
5. the person who's sport is snowboarding is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is handball##5
6. the brazilian is on the left or right of the american##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |      3      |    4     |
| Sport   | badminton  | handball | snowboarding | skateboarding |
| Nationality   | canadian | american | brazilian   | mexican  |

