3. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
4. the person who's hobby is puzzles is somewhere to the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##5
5. the person who growsballoon-flower is somewhere to the left of the person who growsdaisy##5
6. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the person who growsdaisy##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |      3       |     4     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking | puzzles  | singing      | gardening |
| Flower     | balloon-flower    | daisy | amaryllis | orchid   |

