.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-16::.
City: edinburgh, boston, san-francisco, prague
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: classical, electronic, gospel, hip-hop
1. the person traveling to san-francisco is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to prague is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of classical is in an even position##4
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to prague##5
6. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the person traveling to edinburgh and the fan of electronic##2
7. the person traveling to boston is somewhere to the right of the person traveling to edinburgh##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |     3      |     4     |
| City      | edinburgh   | san-francisco  | boston      | prague       |
| Music-Genre   | gospel | hip-hop | electronic | classical |

