.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: lemonade, 7up, iced-tea, sprite
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, jet-ski, quad-bike, snowmobile
1. the person drinking lemonade is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person drinking 7up##2
2. the person driving the helicopter is somewhere to the right of the person drinking sprite##5
3. the person drinking iced-tea is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
4. the person driving the jet-ski is on the left or right of the person driving the helicopter##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |    2    |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage         | iced-tea   | sprite   | lemonade       | 7up   |
| Transport   | quad-bike | jet-ski | helicopter | snowmobile |

