.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-5-20::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: september, july, april, october
The people use 4 different means of transport: car, ship, skateboard, snowmobile
1. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person driving the ship##5
2. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
3. the person driving the skateboard is in an odd position##4
4. the person driving the car is somewhere to the right of the person driving the ship##5
5. the person who's birthday is in july is somewhere to the left of the person driving the snowmobile##5
6. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person driving the car##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3     |     4      |
| Birthday        | july     | october | september | april |
| Transport   | skateboard | snowmobile | ship      | car        |

 